3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of machine learning techniques for automated analysis of femoral artery calcification also falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.ME (Mechanical Engineering): The paper mentions the development of better-informed diagnostic and prognostic tools, which suggests that the research has implications for the field of mechanical engineering, particularly in the design of medical devices.
